snippet: A grandly proportioned 17-room maisonette in a white-glove co-op at 120 East End Avenue opposite Carl Schurz Park is poised to re-enter the market.
abstract: Exclusive column highlights grand, 17-room maisonette in New York City co-op building at 120 East End Avenue near Carl Schurz Park is poised to enter market with asking price of $18 million.
lead_paragraph: A grandly proportioned 17-room maisonette in a white-glove co-op at 120 East End Avenue opposite Carl Schurz Park is poised to re-enter the market.

headline.main: Upper East Side Maisonette for $18 Million
